CHIP: Now grab it and
bring it in, be quick!

02:32.887 --> 02:35.854
AGNES: We got a
shooter and a grabber.

02:36.257 --> 02:38.023
CHIP: We haven't even gotten
a mile down this channel yet,

02:38.042 --> 02:39.591
