02:39.627 --> 02:41.793
AGNES: There it is, Carol.
QUTAN: Right there!
AGNES: One, two, three, go.

02:43.264 --> 02:44.363
CHIP: You're a little high.

02:44.398 --> 02:46.965
You need to bring that front
side down a little bit.

02:47.401 --> 02:49.568
AGNES: Go, Carol.

02:51.772 --> 02:53.272
Yee! You got it.

02:53.307 --> 02:55.007
CHIP: Carol's getting
used to using a .22,

02:55.042 --> 02:57.976
and she's in a boat
doing this while the
muskrat's doing this.

02:58.212 --> 02:59.878
So, when you're doing
this, it's not easy.

02:59.914 --> 03:01.713
Not easy at all.

03:01.749 --> 03:03.081
AGNES: Way up there.

03:03.117 --> 03:05.017
12:00.

03:05.452 --> 03:07.586
CHIP: You lead it too much.

03:08.455 --> 03:10.389
AGNES: Reload.
