03:10.424 --> 03:12.724
By the fifth muskrat,
you'll be just dialed in.

03:13.761 --> 03:14.893
CHIP: Good job, Carol.

03:14.929 --> 03:16.078
AGNES: That's a big one.

03:16.130 --> 03:17.229
CHIP: Wait, wait,
wait, wait, wait.

03:17.264 --> 03:18.396
Right here, right here.

