03:21.235 --> 03:23.969
QUTAN: That one is dead!
AGNES: Nice shot!
MARY: Wonderful!

03:24.004 --> 03:25.504
QUTAN: You got it!
CHIP: There you go.

03:25.539 --> 03:26.838
AGNES: You girls are awesome.
I love this.

