QUTAN: There's one right there.

07:07.327 --> 07:09.194
AGNES: Oh yeah,
theres one right there!

07:09.229 --> 07:10.695
MARY: Right there.

07:10.731 --> 07:12.297
QUTAN: Hey, can
I try to shoot?

07:12.332 --> 07:15.400
AGNES: Carol, pass the gun
to Qutan, let Qutan shoot it.

