CAROL: Good job, Qutan.

07:28.916 --> 07:30.048
CHIP: Good job, Qutan.

07:30.083 --> 07:31.349
I'm glad you got a muskrat.

07:31.385 --> 07:33.452
Now, get a hundred more.

07:33.487 --> 07:35.520
QUTAN: It's gonna pop up.

07:36.457 --> 07:37.789
CAROL: Oh!

07:37.825 --> 07:39.591
AGNES: Qutan got
her second one.

07:39.626 --> 07:40.692
So exciting!

07:40.760 --> 07:42.527
AGNES: We're doing a
real good hunt here.

