how we teach our children
and pretty soon I won't have

07:46.667 --> 07:48.533
to do any shooting anymore.

07:49.903 --> 07:52.604
CAROL: Look, right there.
Good shot!

07:52.606 --> 07:54.139
MARY: You got it!

07:54.174 --> 07:56.975
AGNES: Oh, my god, Qutan!
I can't believe your
proficient shot.

